tweet:
There is a power outage on the North Side of Main St. in Sayville. We have no phone and no internet but we are open! 
Call 631-780-6591 and talk to Mike at Smithtown Running Company if you have any questions. Sorry for the inconvenience PSEG is working on the issue.

At approximately 7:50 p.m. tonight, Prudential Center experienced a brief power outage. Power was quickly restored and tonight’s performance is proceeding as scheduled.
 
Prudential Center has been in close communication with its partner, PSEG, regarding tonight’s brief outage.
That better be the last power outage this weekend. I mean it, PSEG.
There is a power outage in the area of Piermont Ave between Ruckman & Kinderkamack. @PSEGdelivers is aware & responding. If you lost power do not call the HPD. Contact PSEG.
Power outage AGAIN!!! 3 night in a row. PSEG
PSEG launching new power outage notification service http://dlvr.it/PyXZDZ pic.twitter.com/BNC205j2y8
Due to power outage ALL A.M. CLASSES will be cancelled.   We are waiting on PSEG & hope to restore by evening. STAY TUNED.
To report a power outage to PSEG LI: (800) 490-0075 #hamptonshttps://twitter.com/EHStar/status/924930759114346496 …
Power outage in the Ackerman ave wortendyke section of town. If you're without power call PSEG direct NOT the police
Bring in outdoor items that might blow around. If power outage occurs call PSEG directly. https://twitter.com/NWSNewYorkNY/status/922584778041421824 …
Another power outage in #JerseyCity....oh goody! This happens way more frequently than it should. #PSEG #Electricity #Utilities
@PSEGdelivers power outage on Marion ave in Cliffside park, NJ for the past hour. When will the lights turn back on??? #pseg #poweroutage
Pseg Power outage chestnut prospect streets. Overhead transformer blew. 57 houses affected. Pseg said power shld be back 130A. 631-7556900
